snippet.textDisplay:
For Stuntmen react you guys need to do Exorcist and Exorcist 3, the stuntman falling down 93 stone steps!!

In The Exorcist they did it in sequences instead of having the stuntman fall down all 93 stairs at once, but in Exorcist 3 the guy did indeed do all 93 steps...twice!! Super dangerous and even with padding on the stone stairs, you could still easily break bones or your neck. Gives me shivers watching it. Try falling down 5 steps and not getting hurt let alone 93 stone steps twice!
snippet.textOriginal:
For Stuntmen react you guys need to do Exorcist and Exorcist 3, *the stuntman falling down 93 stone steps!!*

In The Exorcist they did it in sequences instead of having the stuntman fall down all 93 stairs at once, but in Exorcist 3 the guy did indeed do all 93 steps...twice!! Super dangerous and even with padding on the stone stairs, you could still easily break bones or your neck. Gives me shivers watching it. Try falling down 5 steps and not getting hurt let alone *93 stone steps twice!*
